items.title: Game of Thrones Wiki
items.headline: Explore the Game of Thrones Wiki
items.desc: Game of Thrones Wiki is the definitive destination for fans of the HBO television series. The wiki documents every episode with loads of details including recaps, memorable quotes, lists of cast, and photo galleries. We have extensive coverage of the world the series takes place in from the characters, noble houses and religions to the geography of the setting.

items.headline: Game of Thrones Wiki
items.desc: Willkommen bei uns im Game of Thrones Wiki! Hier lassen sich alle Informationen rund um die beliebte HBO Serie finden: Von George R. R. Martins Romanreihe "Das Lied von Eis und Feuer", bis hin zu Informationen über die verschiedenen Häuser Targaryen, Stark, Lennister, Baratheon, sämtlichen Charakteren von Arya bis Tyrion und allen Orten von Westeros. Viel Spaß beim Erkunden und Mitmachen!

items.name: Game of Thrones: Ascent Wiki
items.title: Game of Thrones: Ascent Wiki
items.headline: The Social Game based on the HBO television series
items.desc:
Game of Thrones Ascent is an online computer game based on HBO's Game of Thrones television Series.

Created by Disruptor Beam in collaboration with HBO, this game allows you to experience the television series from the point of view of your own character, which has sworn fealty to one of the Great Houses of Westeros; House Bartheon, House Greyjoy, House Lannister, House Martell, House Stark, House Targaryen or House Tyrell.
